---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', item: '/' },
  { name: 'Disclaimer', item: '/disclaimer' }
];
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Disclaimer - CreatorsFeel"
  description="Read the legal disclaimer for CreatorsFeel. Learn about calculator estimate boundaries, third-party link risks, and social platform affiliations."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <article class="legal-page container">
    <header class="legal-header text-center">
      <h1 class="legal-title">Legal Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="legal-date text-muted">Last Updated: June 30, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <h2>1. Affiliation Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        CreatorsFeel is an independent resources platform. CreatorsFeel is **not** affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with YouTube, Google, Instagram, TikTok, Facebook, Meta, or any of their subsidiaries or affiliates.
      </p>
      <p>
        All product names, logos, brands, and trademarks referenced on this website are the property of their respective owners. Their use on CreatorsFeel does not imply any sponsorship or endorsement.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Calculator Estimates & Projections</h2>
      <p>
        All calculations, sponsorship valuations, engagement audit grades, and title scores generated by the tools on CreatorsFeel are **estimates and projections** intended for educational and general informational purposes only.
      </p>
      <p>
        Social media algorithms, audience behavior, and brand sponsorship budgets change constantly. CreatorsFeel does not warrant or guarantee that utilizing these calculations will yield specific revenue, rates, CTR increases, or account growth. Do not make critical legal, career, or financial negotiations solely based on these estimations.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Professional Advice Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The content on this website does not constitute financial, marketing, career, or legal advice. Any reliance you place on the tools or guides on CreatorsFeel is strictly at your own risk. We recommend consulting qualified professionals before entering into legal brand agreements, advertising agreements, or making significant content strategy investments.
      </p>

      <h2>4. External Links Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        CreatorsFeel may contain links to external websites that are not provided or maintained by or in any way affiliated with CreatorsFeel. Please note that CreatorsFeel does not guarantee the accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of any information on these external websites.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        In no event shall CreatorsFeel be liable for any direct, indirect, special, incidental, or consequential damages arising out of your use of, or inability to use, this website, its tools, or its articles.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Consent</h2>
      <p>
        By using our website and tools, you hereby consent to our disclaimer and agree to its terms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: var(--max-width-text);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .legal-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .legal-title {
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .legal-date {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .legal-content {
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
